---
title: polynomial_eval_to_coeff (fulu-polynomial-commitments-sampling)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_roots : roots_of_unity = compute_roots_of_unity(FIELD_ELEMENTS_PER_BLOB)
    q_roots --> q_permute : permuted = bit_reversal_permutation(polynomial)
    q_permute --> q_ifft : result = fft_field(permuted, roots_of_unity, inv=True)
    q_ifft --> [*] : return PolynomialCoeff(result)

    note right of q_roots
        INV: Input polynomial has exactly FIELD_ELEMENTS_PER_BLOB evaluations
        INV: Bit-reversal permutation must be applied before inverse FFT
    end note
